OL,3,CSwansea school to stay closed after
OL,4,Chalf-term due to 'ground movement'
OL,6,FParents at a secondary school in
OL,7,FSwansea have been told the school will
OL,8,Fnot re-open after half-term due to
OL,9,F"ground movement".
OL,11,FBishopston Comprehensive School in
OL,12,FGower is closed this week for the
OL,13,Fscheduled break while investigations
OL,14,Fwere carried out but now it's been
OL,15,Fconfirmed the school will remain
OL,16,Fclosed for another week.
