OL,3,CSwansea school to stay closed after
OL,4,Chalf-term due to 'ground movement'
OL,6,FAn initial post on social media last
OL,7,FFriday (9 February) said: "Due to
OL,8,Fcircumstances outside of our control,
OL,9,Fthe centre will not be open today and
OL,10,Ffor the rest of the weekend.
OL,12,F"We apologise for any inconvenience
OL,13,Fcaused and thank you for your
OL,14,Funderstanding. All of our other
OL,15,Fcentres across Swansea are open as
OL,16,Fusual."
OL,18,Fsaid in a statement: "As a precaution
OL,19,Fsome of the utility supplies have been
OL,20,Fdisconnected which means pupils cannot
OL,21,Freturn after the half-term break.
