OL,4,Chalf-term due to 'ground movement'
OL,6,F"Work is continuing to identify the
OL,7,Fcause and any remedial work required.
OL,9,F"The council and specialist
OL,10,Fcontractors are working to find
OL,11,Falternate solutions to restoring
OL,12,Fsupplies to the school.School staff
OL,13,Fare working on options for providing
OL,14,Feducation to pupils whilst the school
OL,15,Fbuildings are closed.
OL,17,FBishopston Primary School is
OL,18,Funaffected and will reopen as normal
OL,19,Fafter the half-term break.
