OL,6,FThe nearby leisure centre, within a
OL,7,Fseparate building on a different part
OL,8,Fof the site, has its own supplies and
OL,9,Fwill be able to reopen next week."
OL,11,FRobert Smith, Cabinet Member for
OL,12,FEducation, said: "This situation is
OL,13,Fbeyond our control but everything
OL,14,Fpossible is being done to get pupils
OL,15,Fback into class as soon as we can.
OL,17,F"We fully appreciate the temporary
OL,18,Fclosure of the school buildings will
OL,19,Fcause disruption for pupils and their
OL,20,Ffamilies but the safety of pupils and
OL,21,Fstaff is our number one priority.
