OL,6,F"Our teams and contractors are pulling
OL,7,Fout all the stops to get the buildings
OL,8,Freopened as soon as we possibly can
OL,9,Fand we will update pupils and their
OL,10,Ffamilies as soon as we can.
OL,12,F"We will know more once the ground
OL,13,Finvestigations have been completed.
OL,15,F"In the meantime we are working on
OL,16,Foptions for providing education to
OL,17,Fpupils whilst the school buildings
OL,18,Fremain closed and these will be
OL,19,Fdirectly communicated with families.
